{"tid":2206823,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"日經新聞公佈2019相機出貨數據，無反元年","createTime":"2020-09-17T17:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T09:12:46.000Z","uid":296028,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0336585d4c157ff5a54d62d25602d3af13d5782f","tid":2206823,"uid":296028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:35:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://digicame-info.com/2020/09/post-1379.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigicame-info.com%2F2020%2F09%2Fpost-1379.html&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=cd79912d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://digicame-info.com/2020/09/post-1379.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020無反出貨量已佔可換鏡頭相機50%，銷售額佔比65%(代表售出機型價格普遍比單反高)，今年7月同比下降20%，是今年相機市場銷售額唯一阻止了負增長的機種<br />\n<br />\nA7c出現會刺激相機市場疲弱現況，進一步衝擊單反市場<br />\n<br />\nSony相機(包含不可換鏡DC)2019售出300萬台，超越Nikon<br />\n<br />\n2019年可交換鏡頭相機出貨量<br />\nキヤノンCanon：416万台<br />\nニコンNikon：173万台<br />\nソニーSony：166万台<br />\n富士フイルム：50万台<br />\nオリンパス O記：33万台<br />\nその他：28万台<br />\n<br />\n2019年無反相機出貨量<br />\nソニーSony：165万台<br />\nキヤノンcanon：94万台<br />\n富士フイルム：50万台<br />\nオリンパス O記：33万台<br />\nニコンNikon：28万台<br />\nその他：24万台<br />\n<br />\n現在相機市場在手機衝擊下，是2010年的8分1"},{"pid":"d2e0f464f693ab1c904fbd3f02bb29fa365770b8","tid":2206823,"uid":82779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0336585d4c157ff5a54d62d25602d3af13d5782f","tid":2206823,"uid":296028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:35:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://digicame-info.com/2020/09/post-1379.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigicame-info.com%2F2020%2F09%2Fpost-1379.html&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=cd79912d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://digicame-info.com/2020/09/post-1379.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020無反出貨量已佔可換鏡頭相機50%，銷售額佔比65%(代表售出機型價格普遍比單反高)，今年7月同比下降20%，是今年相機市場銷售額唯一阻止了負增長的機種<br />\n<br />\nA7c出現會刺激相機市場疲弱現況，進一步衝擊單反市場<br />\n<br />\nSony相機(包含不可換鏡DC)2019售出3